Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's a bonito stock.\NIt's a gift from Miss Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was HOT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You always apologize right away,\Nbut do you actually feel sorry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you apologize automatically\Nso that you don't get yelled at!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.39,0:02:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly like that. You're just\Nfundamentally too self-deprecating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, that's just his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Just his way?! You're being too soft on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't you been a little\Ntoo soft on Shinji lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you and Mr. Kaji have hooked up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't project your happiness\Non other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing between Kaji and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuragi, I've found a bar\Nthat serves a decent drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How about tonight? Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I've never been involved in\Nan indecent adult relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And here you're acting like a proper guardian?!\NYou hypocrite!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me puke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:50.44,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(451.274,26.499)}{\fs37.5}EPISODE 16: {\fs60}SICKNESS UNTO, DEATH, AND...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,B-type harmonics test, no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Projected adjustment values have been cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You look tired, Miss Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for a lot of private reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how's the Third Child doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that knowing this\Nwill boost his confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, how were my test scores?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! You are Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man! He beat us so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, getting beat that easily\Nis a little frustrating, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's amazing, wonderful,\Nawesome, too awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The great invincible Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This just means we get to\Ntake it easy now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess we should at least\Ndo our best not to be left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:04:00.84,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\frz2.767\c&H000A25&\pos(726.544,622)}Please press this button\Nif you would like to get off
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Next stop is Seisho Kabuse.\NNext stop, Seisho Kabuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Convenient to the Bashar, used books\Nand video game stores...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.34,0:04:40.00,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord\blur1.5\fs97.5\frz19.25\pos(1374,890.501)\c&H080102&\3c&H0B13BC&}ALERT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Five minutes until evacuation of\Nthe Western District is completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is advancing slowly at 2.5 km/hr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What about\Nthe radar observation center at Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't detect it. It just suddenly\Nappeared directly above us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern orange. No AT Field detected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A new kind of Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magi are withholding judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Commander Ikari just had to be gone\Nat a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you all hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've sent you all of the target's data.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all we know right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Approach it carefully and observe its reactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and, if possible, lure it into the airspace\Noutside of the city limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you take point and the other two\Nare backup, got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am?! I think Shinji ought to take point!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a job for the\Nhigh-scoring, utterly fearless,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Number One synch-rate holder, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Or don't you feel up to it, Shin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how it's done, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it, didn't you? "You are Number One!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Combat is a man's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about out of date!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 02 will back him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 00 will back him up as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn kids, running with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's gotten to be quite admirable, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm going to have to chew him out\Nwhen he gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a good guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:25.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,State of Emergency Declared:\NClosed to General Traffic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayanami, Asuka, are you in position yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You know there's no way\Nwe could move that fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.51,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\bord6\blur4.5\pos(612.727,447.5)\c&H212232&\3c&HD5C7DC&\frz338.7\frx18\fry34}Power Source
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead and stop it on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern blue! Angel confirmed!\NDirectly beneath Unit 01!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A shadow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?! It's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, get out of there! Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato? Asuka! Ayanami!\NWhere's the backup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato?! Can you hear me?! Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eject the plug! Send the signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working! No response!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato! Miss Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka! Rei! Rescue Unit 01! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot. What's the point of doing well\Nonly on practice exams?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.99,0:07:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The city!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka, Rei, pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.52,0:08:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 and Ikari are still in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an order. Retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be tough for Major Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They reeled the umbilical cable back in,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but the other end was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much energy\Nin the internal batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Shinji doesn't just\Nflail around with the Eva,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and can hang in there in life support mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,then he can survive for sixteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Tank Platoon deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Hold your current positions and stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sub laser circuit has been opened.\NTransmitting data now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirmed. New line transmitting data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The UN forces have completely surrounded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It stopped spreading once it reached\Na diameter of just over 600 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But are the ground troops going to be any use?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.50,0:09:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They think they're applying pressure on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking matters into his own hands,\Nignoring the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, talk about getting what he deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because he got a little better score\Non yesterday's tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he was going to show me how it's done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big-headed idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is my bad-mouthing of Shinji\Nthat much of a problem for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you pilot Eva just for the praise of others?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Not of others! I do it because\NI want to be able to praise myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, he went out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll just have to scold him\Nwhen he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought sleeping\Ncould be this exhausting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No radar or sonar reflections at all.\NThis space must be too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been twelve hours since\NI switched to life-support mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So my life will end in another four or five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that shadow is actually the Angel's body?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. It's six hundred eighty\Nmeters in diameter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,with a thickness of three nanometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultra-thin space is supported by\Nan inwardly-directed AT Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The inside is an imaginary space,\Ncalled a Sea of Dirac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's probably connected\Nto another universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the sphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappears when the imaginary circuit\Nof the body closes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The object in the sky is the real shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So the black shadow that swallowed\NUnit 01 is the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no way that we can fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is getting cloudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The purification system is giving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood! It smells of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I don't want to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't I open the lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up! Let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato! Asuka! Ayanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.65,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, someone help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A forced Eva salvage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only possibility that might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We would drop all 992 existing\NN2 mines into its center,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,while simultaneously activating the\NAT Fields of the remaining Evas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,disrupting the Angel's imaginary circuit\Nfor one millisecond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In that instant, we'll concentrate\Nall the explosive energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroy the Angel along\Nwith the Sea of Dirac that forms it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But with that, the body of the Eva...\NThere's no telling what would happen to Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be called a rescue operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This operation's top priority is\Nto recover Unit 01 itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavy damage to the body is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, the pilot's life is not our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If Shinji's lost, it's your fault. Don't forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you and Commander Ikari\Nso worried about Unit 01?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the hell is an Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.17,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've given you all the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.34,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking command of this entire operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be sending some flights to\NKansai International Airport as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact Air Traffic Control and the\NJADF's Air Transport divisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second Impact, the\NInstrumentality Project, Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still secrets that I'm in the dark about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am you. People have another\Nself within themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The self is always composed of two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The self which is actually seen,\Nand the self observing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many entities called Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The other Shinji Ikari that exists in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shinji Ikari in Misato Katsuragi's mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.12,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the Shinji in Asuka Sohryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,the Shinji in Rei Ayanami,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Shinji in Gendo Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All are different Shinji Ikaris,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but each of them is a true Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are afraid of those Shinji Ikaris\Nin other people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid of other people hating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of being hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is at fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Father is the one who is at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The father who deserted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go, always immediately thinking\Nthat it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I say you're self-deprecating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You just believe that you can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have faith in your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I hate him, but now I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My father called me by my name.\NI was praised by my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to spend the rest of your life\Nruminating on that happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I believe in those words, I can keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As you continue to deceive yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody does it!\NThat's how everyone survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe that you're fine with the way things are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or you won't be able to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much hardship in this world\Nfor me to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, the fact you can't swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't made to float!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That is self-deception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you call it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shut your eyes and turned a deaf ear\Nto the things you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,His sister was injured during the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the others say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want to hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You're running away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you can live by linking\Njust the enjoyable moments like a rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found something I enjoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Finding something you enjoy\Nand doing nothing but that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In theory, the entry plug's energy reserves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,should be reaching their expiration point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The plug suit's life support system\Nwill be getting close to redline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance the schedule by twelve minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it while there's a chance\Nthat Shinji's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, am I unwanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! He may be guilty\Nof killing his own wife!
