Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a very praiseworthy thing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, you must not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.38,0:17:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The heating and the oxygen circulation\Nare already out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless, the suit is giving out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.95,0:18:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Evas are in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,AT field generation ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixty seconds to mine drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.31,0:18:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All meters and gauges are going off the scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But we haven't done anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01's power level is zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm piloting something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind... what kind of monster\Nhave we copied from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that the Evas aren't just\Ncopies of the First Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what is Nerv going to do with them\Nonce all the Angels have been destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?! Shinji?! Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji?! Are you all right, Shinji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to scold him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never thought these Evas\Nwere as frightening as I did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the Evas really on our side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They may hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that Major Katsuragi\Nmay have noticed something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Let her be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If Rei or Shinji were to find out the Eva's secrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,they'd never forgive us, would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay in bed for today.\NWe'll take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.55,0:21:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of blood won't come off.
